## 1. System Overview

KrishiSaathi is a distributed, three-tier system composed of:

1. **React Frontend** вҖ” SPA served via Vercel (CDN)
2. **Node.js/Express Backend API** вҖ” REST + WebSocket server on Render
3. **Python FastAPI AI Microservice** вҖ” ML inference service on Render

All three communicate over HTTPS. The frontend calls the backend REST API and receives real-time events via Socket.IO. The backend proxies AI detection requests to the AI microservice.

