### 3.4 Key Frontend Patterns
- JWT stored in `localStorage`; injected via Axios request interceptor
- `AuthContext` wraps entire app; provides `user`, `login()`, `logout()`
- i18next initialized with language detection from browser/localStorage
- Socket.IO connection established on marketplace page mount
- All API errors handled centrally in Axios response interceptor

