## 7. Security Requirements

| Layer | Implementation |
|---|---|
| Transport | HTTPS/TLS enforced on all services |
| Authentication | JWT (HS256), 7-day expiry, httpOnly refresh (future) |
| Password hashing | bcryptjs, 10 salt rounds |
| Input validation | express-validator on all POST/PUT endpoints |
| Rate limiting | 100 req/15min per IP via express-rate-limit |
| CORS | Whitelist: CLIENT_URL only |
| Image uploads | File type validation (image/jpeg, image/png, image/webp only) |
| MongoDB injection | Mongoose schema validation + sanitization |
| API keys | All secrets in environment variables, never in code |

